I just got here ...what 'double standards' currently exist again?  I forgot.  Is that the double standard of teaming on a non-rotation mob (which is clearly covered as acceptable under the easily understood and written 'FCFS' convention ...you know, I gotta be pulling something outta my ass in every fun filled post!) ...or is that the double standard of applying rotation mob rules to non-rotation mobs by 'extrapolation'?<br>
